original: Larsson, Aron Gottfrid, teol. o. fil. kand., kyrkoherde, Mjöbäck, f. 8/1/90 i Enslöv, Hall. 1. G. 24 m. Anna Wic-kander. — Teol. kand., fil. kand. V. pastor i Stenkyrka 23, kommin. i Lia-red 23-33, kyrkoh. i Mjöbäck ir. 33. Ordf. i past :kyrkostämma, skolstyr., huvudm. i Mjöbäcks past. sparb., led. av Sparb:styr., av komm:furim.
translated: Larsson, Aron Gottfrid, Bachelor of Theology and Philosophy, clergyman, Mjöbäck, born on January 8th, 1890 in Enslöv, Halland. First marriage on January 24th, with Anna Wickander. - Bachelor of Theology, Bachelor of Philosophy. Vice pastor in Stenkyrka until 1923, curate in Ljungred from 1923-1933, vicar in Mjöbäck from 1933. Chairman of the parish council, school board, headmaster of Mjöbäck's vicarage savings bank, member of the Savings Bank board, and municipal commissioner.
